Name: Dungeon Bosses
About the game: The brother of the main character accidentally falls into the dungeon and the protagonist has to go to the rescue. At the beginning of the game, you can learn a little plot that would have a small idea, but the ending of the game will depend only you, whether it is good or bad end. The game has 13 bosses and they need to go through, pumping your character, that would eventually release the brother of the protagonist. Features:   13 bosses   Various items for leveling   Getting statuettes when the necessary conditions   Interesting story
